    "causal_summary": "The five skills duplicate generic plumbing — a byte-identical runtime-capabilities resolver in deep-research and deep-review, a loop-lock CLI adapter only in deep-context, re-inlined atomic-write/jsonl-repair mirrors across four reducers, and resolveArtifactRoot/emitResourceMap imported from system-spec-kit/shared (so the two-skill architecture is not self-contained). The terminal journal taxonomy is frozen only inside deep-improvement. Left duplicated, these constants drift; promoting them is a prerequisite for a thin hub and a self-contained backend.",
